Jacqueline ThomasThomas is responsible for providing strategic direction and leadership over multiple departments, including internal audit, compliance and ethics, regulatory compliance, customs/trade compliance, and assurance. Her division ensures compliance with laws, regulations and internal policies and procedures upholding Toyota&#x2019;s commitment to integrity and principled performance. Thomas will continue to report to Jim Lentz, chief executive officer, TMNA. Prior to her new position, Thomas served as vice president, chief compliance officer for TMNA.